Package: afrobarometer.cleaning
Title: Clean and Harmonize Afrobarometer Survey Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Your", "Name", email = "you@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to load, clean, and harmonize Afrobarometer
    survey data across rounds 5 to 9. Handles round-specific variable name
    differences, recodes negative/sentinel values from the Afrobarometer
    codebook to NA, binarizes selected variables, and computes composite
    indices (civic participation, bribes, services, etc.).
